<div id="frontpage-intro">
  <div id="frontpage-intro-lead">
    <div class="frontpage-lead-cell">
      <h2>
        <%= _("Exercise your right to know.") %>
      </h2>
      <p class="frontpage-lead-text">
        <%= _("To get information from public authorities:") %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="frontpage-lead-cell">
      <p class="frontpage-lead-enum">
        1
      </p>
      <p class="frontpage-lead-text">
        <%= _("Think of a question for a public authority.") %>
      </p><span id="frontpage-lead-button">
      <%= link_to _("Ask") + " »", list_public_bodies_default_path %></span>
    </div>
    <div class="frontpage-lead-cell">
      <p class="frontpage-lead-enum">
        2
      </p>
      <p class="frontpage-lead-text">
        <%= _("We send the question for you") %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="frontpage-lead-cell">
      <p class="frontpage-lead-enum">
        3
      </p>
      <p class="frontpage-lead-text">
        <%= _("We'll notify you when there is an answer.") %>
      </p><%= link_to _("Will they answer?") + "»", help_requesting_path(:anchor => 'making_requests') %>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div id="frontpage-intro-sidebar">
    <div id="frontpage-lead-ad">
      <h4>
        Informe De Tu Derecho a Preguntar
      </h4>
      <p>
        De las 300 solicitudes de información válidas recibidas durante 2014, sólo 84 (13%) recibieron una respuesta válida. El silencio administrativo, la mayor problema para el derecho de acceso a la información en Nicaragua, es del 80%. <a href="">Lee nuestro informe completo</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="frontpage-content">
  <div id="frontpage-search-box">
    <div id="frontpage-search-label">
      <h4>
        <%=  _("Search over requests and authorities:") %>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="frontpage-search-form">
      <%= form_tag({:action => "search_redirect"}, {:id => "search_form"}) do %>
      <div>
        <%= text_field_tag 'query', params[:query], { :size => 80 } %><%= submit_tag _('Search') %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


